com.opentok.android
Class Subscriber

java.lang.Object
  com.opentok.android.Subscriber

public abstract class Subscriber
extends java.lang.Object

Consumes audio and video of a publisher in the OpenTok session. Subscribers are created by passing a valid Stream instance into Subscriber#newInstance(android.content.Context, com.opentok.android.Stream) and can connect to receive media with Session.subscribe(com.opentok.android.Subscriber).
